---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms - Moaiy" description="Terms for using moaiy.com resources and releases.">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-bg-primary py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">Terms</h1>
      <p class="font-body text-text-tertiary text-sm mb-8">Last updated: 2026-03-31</p>

      <div class="space-y-6 font-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Use Of Website</h2>
          <p>
            The website provides project information, documentation links, and release navigation.
            Use it lawfully and do not attempt to abuse, disrupt, or attack the service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Open Source Licensing</h2>
          <p>
            The Moaiy application repository is distributed under the MIT License.
            Refer to the repository license file for authoritative terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">No Warranty</h2>
          <p>
            Software and website content are provided "as is" without warranties. You are responsible for
            evaluating suitability, safeguarding keys, and maintaining secure backups.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>
            The website may link to third-party services (for example GitHub). Their terms and privacy policies apply
            when you use those services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about these terms: <a href="mailto:support@moaiy.com" class="text-accent-primary hover:underline">support@moaiy.com</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
